{
  "chapter": 71,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十一回 柳暗花明：铁萍姑与小鱼儿被困山洞，铁萍姑向小鱼儿倾诉心声，两人关系升温。小鱼儿发现老鼠引路，找到出口，意外发现江玉郎藏匿的段合肥赃银。小鱼儿与铁萍姑躲在暗处，观察江玉郎与轩辕三光以老鼠叼肉为赌注的奇特赌博。小鱼儿识破江玉郎利用铜灯操纵赌博结果的诡计，及时阻止轩辕三光上当。江玉郎以慕容九妹为人质威胁，小鱼儿现身揭露其阴谋，最终江玉郎劫持慕容九妹作为要挟。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "人生，人生真是多么奇妙，我现在才知道……我两三天前还不认得你，但现在……现在……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你可知道，我现在想什么？我现在最想瞧瞧你的脸。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不要……求求你不要……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "火折子……快没有了……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "火折子虽然珍贵，但能瞧见你现在这模样，无论牺牲多么珍贵的东西，都是值得的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "只可惜现在没有镜子，否则我也要让你知道，你现在的模样，要比以前那种冷冰冰的样子美丽多了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我们若真的走不出去，你会怪我么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "怪你？我怎会怪你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你在那里，本还不会死的，但现在……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "若这么说，你本该怪我才是，若不是我，你又怎会受这样的苦？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "受苦？……你可知道，我一生中从没有比现在快乐过。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "连我自己都已不将我当做女人，何况别人呢？别人也许会将我看成仙子甚至魔女，却绝不会将我看成女人的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "但你却不折不扣是个女人，我可以用一千种法子来证明。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我现在自己也知道了，所以我现在就算死，也是快乐的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我也知道，你这样对我，并不是真的喜欢我，只不过是为了安慰我，让我得到最后的快乐。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你……你想得太多了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但我还是感激你的，我只是……只是真的累了，求求你让我睡吧，这一睡纵然永不醒来，我也满足了……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你不必睡，我们已得救了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但这只不过是些老鼠。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你瞧，这些老鼠又肥又大，绝对不是在山腹里的，这里连一颗米都没有，绝对养不了这么肥的老鼠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你说这些老鼠是从山外跑进来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "不错，这里必定已接近山腹的边缘，出路必定就在附近。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我又不是财迷，老天却偏偏总是要我发现一些神秘的宝藏，我真不懂，世上的宝藏怎会有这么多。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这里并不是什么神秘的宝藏。这些箱子搬进来，还没有几天，上面连积灰都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "到了此刻，你还是比我仔细得多。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "外面有人！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这石头有什么好看的，这两人为何看得如此出神？莫非是疯子不成。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "据我所知这人非但不疯，而且头脑还比别人都清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那么他们为什么死盯着这块石头呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "也许他们希望这石头上能长出花来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我以前是知道这小子没毛病的，但现在却说不定了，难道他竟忘了肉是用嘴吃的，不是用眼睛看的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若认得他，不如去教教他吧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我又何尝不想去教他吃肉，只可惜我现在只要一走出去，他就要吃我的肉了，他早已恨不得吃我的肉了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "另外一个人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "这人我还瞧不出是谁，好像是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "好，这一次又是你赢了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "现在，你已欠我一百三十万两，你那里面的东西，已快输光了吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你放心，还多着哩。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "老子正赌得过瘾，你若这么快就输光，老子不捏出你蛋黄来才怪。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "原来这两人是在赌钱，谁面前的肉被老鼠衔走，谁就赢了，这样的赌法，倒也是天下少有。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "但这样的赌法却公平得很，谁也休想作弊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "若是老鼠不来，怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "老鼠不来，反正就等着。这人的赌瘾最大，只要是在赌，你就叫他等八天八夜也没什么关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，此刻看来他们就已不止赌了八天八夜了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你可要知道背对着我们的这人是谁么？他就是‘恶赌鬼’轩辕三光！不赌到人光、钱光，他是绝不肯站起来走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "恶赌鬼？莫非是十大恶人中的？……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可知道这‘十大恶人’究竟是些什么人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你这话可算真问对人了，世上比我更知道十大恶人的，还真不多。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "十大恶人就是‘血手’杜杀、‘笑里藏刀’哈哈儿、‘不男不女’屠娇娇、‘半人半鬼’阴九幽、‘不吃人头’李大嘴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "还有‘狂狮’铁战、‘迷死人不赔命’萧咪咪、‘恶赌鬼’轩辕三光、‘损人不利己’白开心，再加上欧阳丁、欧阳当兄弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "照你这样说来，岂非有十一个人了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "只因这欧阳兄弟向来秤不离锤，锤不离秤，两个人无论干什么，都是在一起的，所以只能算作一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这些人是否真的都十分恶毒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "其实世上比他们更恶毒的人，还不知有多少，只不过，这些人做事特别不正常，毛病特别大而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这话是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "譬如说，这‘不吃人头’李大嘴，平日看来，他不但很和气，而且还可说是个文武双全的才子，但他毛病一发作起来，却连自己的老婆都能吃下肚去，见过他面的人，谁也想不到他做得出这种事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你难道认得他们的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我非但认得他们，老实告诉你，我还是跟着他们长大的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你可知道他们现在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "只怕是在龟山一带……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你为何问得这么清楚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我只不过是好奇而已，谁想得到世上有这么奇怪的人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你我已赌了七八天，还是谁也没有输光，你不烦么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不烦，不烦，再赌上三年六个月，老子也不会烦的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "但这样赌下去，我却有些烦了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你烦，也要陪老子赌下去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "我并不是说不赌，只不过是想将赌注增大而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "老子赌钱，向来是嫌小不嫌大，越大越过瘾，你要赌多大，说吧。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "阁下身上带的东西，既然值七八十万两，此刻又赢了我一百三十万两，你我这一注，就赌两百万两吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "一注见输赢，这倒也痛快，只是……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "老子早已看过，你那洞里最多也不过只有两三百万，此刻已输了一半，你那里还有这么多银子来跟老子赌？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "洞中存银，至少还有一百万。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "还差一百万呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "还差一百万，以人来作数。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "格老子，就凭你这龟儿子，也值得了一百万？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "在下纵不值一百万，却有值一百万的人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "阁下难道还要先估估价么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "当然要先估估价，上了赌桌六亲不认，就算是儿子跟老子赌钱，帐也要算清楚的，一文钱也差错不得。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "既是如此，在下这就去将她带来就是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "阁下但请放心，在下立刻就回来的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "老子自然放心得很，你龟儿子家当都在这里，又急着想翻本，不回来才怪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这些人赌起钱来，一赌就是上百万两银子，他们的银子简直好像是偷来的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "纵然是偷来的，也要费些力气，一下子就输出去，岂不可惜。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "这就叫来得容易去得快。何况，一个好赌的人，连老婆儿子输出去，都不会心疼的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "只是我未想到，这江玉郎竟也是个赌鬼，输光了还不甘心，还要把人押给别人来赌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "难道他也要把老婆拿来和别人赌么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "他就算有老婆，也不值一百万，这小子到底在玩什么花样，就连我也猜不出了，能值一百万的人，到底不多呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你怎地带来个女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "当然是女人，若是男人，就不值钱了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但从你这龟儿子手上送出来的剩货，只怕连一文都不值。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这位姑娘虽然跟着我走了几天，但我却绝未动过她的毫发。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你这馋猫会不偷吃，老子不信。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "阁下若不信，一试便知。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子又想搞什么鬼？他将这盏灯带进带出，绝不会没有用意的。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "美女，果然是个美女，只可惜近二十年来，老子已对任何美女都不感兴趣了，你还是带她走吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这位姑娘虽美，但值钱的地方却不在她这张脸上，在她的身分。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "她难道还是位公主不成？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "虽不是公主，却也和公主差不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "她究竟是谁？你这龟儿子说话怎地总要兜圈子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "她便是九秀山庄的慕容九妹姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "慕容永的九姑娘，怎会落在你手里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "她被恶人所害，神智迷失，不知下落，慕容家的八位姊妹、八位姑爷，用尽千方百计，都寻她不着，在下运气好，却在无意中找到了她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "阁下请想想，若有人将她送回她姐姐、姐夫那里去，秦剑、南宫柳等人又将如何感激，那谢礼还会少得了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好，老子就跟你赌了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "赌不得！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你跟我出去，喜欢吃什么，就拿起来吃，千万莫要客气，我现在已有对付这小子的法子。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "躲在粪坑下吃大便的朋友，难道已忘了我么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你怎会在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "老子阴魂不散，跟定了你这龟儿子了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "若是别人从里面钻出来，老子也要吃一惊，但你这鬼精灵，就算从地下钻出来，老子也不会奇怪的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小兄弟，老子赌了一辈子，这次你为何说老子赌不得？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "只因你一赌，就要上当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "老子是老赌鬼，这龟儿子顶多也不过算是个小赌鬼，他怎能令老子上当？何况这赌法最公平不过，谁也作不得弊，除非他也是个老鼠精。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你说这赌法最公平，你也赢了许多次了，是么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你可知道你是怎么赢的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "老子这两天运气好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "难道还有什么别的原因不成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "只因为……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "不行，我不能说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你为何不能说？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这两天我体力不好，我怕这小子来跟我拼命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这龟儿子若是敢动你一根手指，老子不把他骨头一根根拆散才怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "我若和他打架，你帮我忙么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "好，这样我才能放心说了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你总该知道，老鼠最怕光亮的，到了晚上，才敢露面，但只要一点起灯，它们就没有戏唱了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "想不到你对老鼠们也了解得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "鱼和老鼠，正是同病相怜，一见到猫就头疼，我不了解它们谁了解？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但这……这又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这里的老鼠，想必都是刚从外面搬进来的，外面只怕是来了只恶猫，把它们赶进了洞，谁知这山洞里并没有老鼠饭店，它们若非快饿疯了，也不敢到你们面前来抢肉吃的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这还要老子不动，谁若忍不住要动，老鼠就不敢来吃他面前的肉了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "但你还忘了一点，方才这盏灯，是在你身后，你的身子挡住了灯光，那块肉便落在黑影里。老鼠怕光，只敢来吃黑暗中的肉，所以你才会连赢几次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "果然不错，你果然是个鬼精灵，连这种事都想得到。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "老子懂了，这龟儿子现在已把灯换了个地方，这灯光正好照在老子面前的肉上，他算定老子这一次要输。所以才要赌大的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "正是如此，他现在不但可以把输了的银子捞回来，还可捞你一票。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "若不是你来提醒，老子今天竟要在阴沟里翻船了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "如何？我说的不错吧？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你定要以小人之心度君子之腹我也没法子．",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "江玉郎，你那一肚子坏水，别人不知道，我还会不知道么？你在我面前，还装什么蒜。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我只怕是时运不济，才会遇见了鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不错，你遇着了我，当真是倒了八辈子霉了，如今我人赃并获，你就跟我到段合肥那里说话吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "事已至今，我也没话说了，只不过……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只不过你们还想要这位慕容姑娘的命么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    }
  ],
